      <title>Meta 洽谈入股雷朋眼镜制造商 推进智能眼镜业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meta-explores-multibillion-euro-stake-in-ray-ban-maker-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 Facebook 所有者加大对智能眼镜的开发力度，Meta Platforms Inc. 正在洽谈收购雷朋太阳镜制造商的少数股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/meta-explores-multibillion-euro-stake-in-ray-ban-maker-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孩之宝任命微软的 John Hight 领导巫师部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/hasbro-names-microsoft-s-john-hight-to-lead-wizards-division</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份内部备忘录显示，孩之宝公司任命资深视频游戏高管约翰·海特（John Hight）为威世智和数字游戏部门总裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/hasbro-names-microsoft-s-john-hight-to-lead-wizards-division</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥特曼斥资 37 亿美元创办核聚变初创企业 让科学家们困惑不已</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sam-altman-s-helion-energy-promises-fusion-power-by-2028</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 OpenAI 亿万富翁 CEO 的大力支持下，Helion Energy 承诺将在 2028 年前建成一座核聚变发电厂。迄今为止，其成果仍是一个谜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/sam-altman-s-helion-energy-promises-fusion-power-by-2028</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix 多头押注《布里奇顿》将保持订阅用户增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/netflix-bulls-bet-on-bridgerton-keeping-subscriber-gains-going</link>
      <description><![CDATA[流媒体巨头 Netflix Inc. 的多头一直在其业绩公布前上调其目标价，押注《布里奇顿》等热门剧集将保持用户数量的强劲增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/netflix-bulls-bet-on-bridgerton-keeping-subscriber-gains-going</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 11:59:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌将领投移动初创公司 Glance 的 2.5 亿美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/google-set-to-lead-250-million-round-by-mobile-startup-glance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[移动内容提供商 Glance 正在进行深入谈判，希望在由现有支持者谷歌领投的一轮融资中筹集资金，此举将使这家印度初创公司扩大其影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/google-set-to-lead-250-million-round-by-mobile-startup-glance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 11:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>客户增加软件支出，印孚瑟斯上调销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-as-clients-boost-software-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印孚瑟斯有限公司 (Infosys Ltd.) 上调了今年的销售预期，表明在全球经济复苏的推动下，客户正逐渐开始增加技术支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/infosys-raises-sales-forecast-as-clients-boost-software-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:10:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>梅赛德斯与 Stellantis 洽谈支持塞尔维亚锂计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/mercedes-stellantis-in-talks-to-back-serbia-s-lithium-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[梅赛德斯-奔驰集团和 Stellantis NV 正在与塞尔维亚政府讨论投资锂加工和电动汽车电池生产，这可能会为欧洲最大的锂矿提供新的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/mercedes-stellantis-in-talks-to-back-serbia-s-lithium-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:05:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜黑客涉嫌盗窃 2.35 亿美元加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/wazirx-pauses-crypto-rupee-withdrawals-after-wallet-breach-lyqzzwm1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度加密货币交易所 WazirX 表示，在发现其中一个钱包遭到入侵后，该公司暂停了平台的提款业务，分析人士怀疑此次攻击是朝鲜黑客所为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/wazirx-pauses-crypto-rupee-withdrawals-after-wallet-breach-lyqzzwm1</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:17:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>与假拜登自动拨号电话有关的人工智能初创公司旨在打击滥用行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/elevenlabs-partners-with-reality-defender-to-combat-deepfake-audio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ElevenLabs 是一家利用人工智能克隆人类声音的初创公司，它正在与一项人工智能检测服务合作，以对抗关键选举年期间日益加剧的深度伪造威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/elevenlabs-partners-with-reality-defender-to-combat-deepfake-audio</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电上调营收预期，反映人工智能需求旺盛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tsmc-s-profit-surpasses-estimates-after-ai-investment-surges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾半导体制造股份有限公司 (Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co.) 季度业绩超出预期后，该公司上调了 2024 年收入增长预测，反映出其对全球人工智能支出热潮能够持续的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tsmc-s-profit-surpasses-estimates-after-ai-investment-surges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
